msgid "Using NavigationMaps"
msgstr "使用 NavigationMap"

msgid ""
"A NavigationMap is an abstract navigation world on the NavigationServer "
"identified by a NavigationServer :ref:`RID<class_RID>`."
msgstr ""
"NavigationMap 是 NavigationServer 上的抽象導航世界，並以 NavigationServer "
"的 :ref:`RID<class_RID>` 作為識別。"

msgid ""
"A map can hold and connect a near infinite number of navigation regions with "
"navigation meshes to build the traversable areas of a game world for "
"pathfinding."
msgstr ""
"導航地圖可以容納並連接近乎無限數量的導航區域和導航網格，以構建遊戲世界中可行"
"走的區域，提供路徑尋找功能。"

msgid ""
"A map can contain avoidance agents. Collision avoidance will be calculated "
"based on the agents present in the map."
msgstr "導航地圖可以包含避障代理。碰撞避免會根據地圖中存在的代理進行計算。"

msgid ""
"Different NavigationMaps are completely isolated from each other but "
"navigation regions and avoidance agents can switch between different maps. "
"Switches will become effective on NavigationServer synchronization."
msgstr ""
"不同的導航地圖彼此完全獨立，但導航區域與避障代理可以在不同地圖間切換。切換動"
"作會在 NavigationServer 同步時生效。"

msgid "Default navigation maps"
msgstr "預設導航地圖"

msgid ""
"By default Godot creates a navigation map for "
"each :ref:`World2D<class_World2D>` and :ref:`World3D<class_World3D>` of the "
"root viewport."
msgstr ""
"預設情況下，Godot 會為根視窗的每個 :ref:`World2D<class_World2D>` "
"與 :ref:`World3D<class_World3D>` 建立一個導航地圖。"

msgid ""
"The 2D default navigation map RID can be obtained with "
"``get_world_2d().get_navigation_map()`` from any :ref:`Node2D<class_Node2D>` "
"inheriting Node."
msgstr ""
"2D 預設導航地圖的 RID 可以透過任何繼承 Node 的 :ref:`Node2D<class_Node2D>` 使"
"用 ``get_world_2d().get_navigation_map()`` 取得。"

msgid ""
"The 3D default navigation map RID can be obtained with "
"``get_world_3d().get_navigation_map()`` from any :ref:`Node3D<class_Node3D>` "
"inheriting Node."
msgstr ""
"3D 預設導航地圖的 RID 可以透過任何繼承 Node 的 :ref:`Node3D<class_Node3D>` 使"
"用 ``get_world_3d().get_navigation_map()`` 取得。"

msgid "Creating new navigation maps"
msgstr "建立新導航地圖"

msgid ""
"The NavigationServer can create and support as many navigation maps as "
"required for specific gameplay. Additional navigation maps are created and "
"handled by using the NavigationServer API directly e.g. to support different "
"avoidance agent or actor locomotion types."
msgstr ""
"NavigationServer 可以根據遊戲需求建立及支援任意數量的導航地圖。若需支援不同的"
"避障代理或角色移動類型，可以直接使用 NavigationServer API 來建立與管理額外的"
"導航地圖。"

msgid ""
"For example uses of different navigation maps "
"see :ref:`doc_navigation_different_actor_types` "
"and :ref:`doc_navigation_different_actor_locomotion`."
msgstr ""
"有關不同導航地圖的應用範例，請參"
"閱 :ref:`doc_navigation_different_actor_types` "
"及 :ref:`doc_navigation_different_actor_locomotion`。"

msgid ""
"Each navigation map individually synchronizes queued changes to its "
"navigation regions and avoidance agents. A navigation map that has not "
"received changes will consume little to no processing time. Navigation "
"regions and avoidance agents can only be part of a single navigation map but "
"they can switch map at any time."
msgstr ""
"每個導航地圖會獨立同步其導航區域和避障代理的變更佇列。未發生變更的導航地圖幾"
"乎不會消耗處理時間。導航區域與避障代理僅能隸屬於單一導航地圖，但可隨時切換至"
"其他地圖。"

msgid ""
"A navigation map switch will take effect only after the next "
"NavigationServer synchronization."
msgstr "導航地圖的切換僅會在下次 NavigationServer 同步時生效。"

msgid ""
"There is no difference between navigation maps created with the "
"NavigationServer2D API or the NavigationServer3D API."
msgstr ""
"使用 NavigationServer2D API 或 NavigationServer3D API 建立的導航地圖沒有任何"
"差異。"
